      <title>摩根大通任命 Garcia-Salas 和 Redmond 负责中型股投资银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-appoints-garcia-salas-redmond-mid-cap-investment-banking-2024-09-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社看到的一份备忘录显示，摩根大通已聘请 Humberto Garcia-Salas 和 Andrew Redmond 担任中型投资银行部门董事总经理，以进一步加强其投资银行业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-appoints-garcia-salas-redmond-mid-cap-investment-banking-2024-09-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:26:17 GMT</pubDate>
