      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/keycorp-sells-nearly-7-bln-low-yield-investments-2024-09-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国地区性银行KeyCorp周一表示，已出售约70亿美元的低收益投资，该交易将导致第三季度税后损失约7亿美元。]]></description>
